{"tid":713616,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"小學雞數學問題","createTime":"2018-06-23T03:34:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-23T08:13:56.000Z","uid":76159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ade1dc0a23453b29d39da25f58a0d9e72779ffd9","tid":713616,"uid":76159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T03:34:58.000Z","msg":"點解將多位數的數字加埋就知除唔除得盡3<br />\n好似26889 加埋33 就知除得盡3? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：小學雞都不如"},{"pid":"76ffbb8c9e776ab2961192119247917800fae291","tid":713616,"uid":4880,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T03:36:59.000Z","msg":"會唔會連中文都有問題"},{"pid":"f39f67d08ea2262993718bb91056932fa6ae261c","tid":713616,"uid":69098,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T03:38:32.000Z","msg":"因為咁啱26889+33出嚟既數咁啱係3既倍數<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33f7008976cd339475c13ce5829812f5f3d84275","tid":713616,"uid":90820,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T03:45:59.000Z","msg":"以數字 abc為例<br />\nabc = 100*a + 10*b + c<br />\n=99*a + 9*b +(a+b+c) <br />\n=9(11*a+1*b) +(a+b+c)<br />\n<br />\n因為 9(11*a+1*b+c) 可被 3 整除，因此，只需要考慮 (a+b+c) 是否同樣可被 3 整除即可。<br />\n<br />\nGoogle答到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eda985732dbb52e2f2c6e23fc75daade34f2b6a6","tid":713616,"uid":137768,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T03:55:44.000Z","msg":"兩位數case:<br />\n(a*10+b)mod 3 = 0<br />\n[(a*10 mod 3) + (b mod 3)] mod 3=0<br />\n<br />\nwhere<br />\na*10 mod 3 = [(a mod 3)(10 mod 3)] mod 3<br />\n                       = (a mod 3) mod 3<br />\n                       = a mod 3<br />\n<br />\nThus,<br />\n[(a mod 3) + (b mod 3)] mod 3 = 0<br />\n(a+b) mod 3 = 0"},{"pid":"108b040eb5f1a076f98e150a17a322ec0ad73630","tid":713616,"uid":15483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score